    <title>Davis-Bacon Repeal Act</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-09-24T15:46:32Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Davis-Bacon Repeal Act</b></p> <p> Repeals the Davis-Bacon Act (which requires that the locally prevailing wage rate be paid to various classes of laborers and mechanics working under federally-financed or federally-assisted contracts for construction, alteration, and repair of public buildings or public works).</p> <p>States that references in any law to a wage requirement of the Davis-Bacon Act shall be null and void. </p> </p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2015-07-16</actionDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
